## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="d6f65-102"><xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlLink>控件允许进行编程访问的 html`link`服务器上的元素。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6f65-102">The <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlLink> control allows programmatic access to the HTML `link` element on the server.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6f65-103"><xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlLink>控件可以用于以编程方式在网页中指定的级联样式表 (CSS) 引用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6f65-103">The <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlLink> control can be used to programmatically specify a cascading style sheet (CSS) reference in a Web page.</span></span>  
  
   
  
